{"tid":2134510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情下污染物勁減3成令空氣清新 東涌居民：無咗鼻竇炎","createTime":"2020-07-31T18:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T01:58:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbadeb2cadf5c88c938e0cddda05ff3fc42f108","tid":2134510,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200801/6JL2GRBT66ANGAOKU5JG6VMRK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200801%2F6JL2GRBT66ANGAOKU5JG6VMRK4%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=e33d6398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200801%2F6JL2GRBT66ANGAOKU5JG6VMRK4%2F&h=3475679a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200801/6JL2GRBT66ANGAOKU5JG6VMRK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n各國因為疫情令經濟、人類活動減少，空氣質素得而改善。《蘋果》統計香港今年首季空氣污染物數據，發現16個空氣監測站大部份污染物濃度較去年同期下降，僅臭氧有輕微上升。各區空氣污染物以東涌跌幅最大，荃灣次之。有東涌居民以往受鼻敏感和鼻竇炎困擾，今年罕有沒有發病，形容疫情帶來短暫清新空氣。"},{"pid":"613550db0bc8fc5837640d9a66e1ab50da4396dd","tid":2134510,"uid":232157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"天空靚咗"},{"pid":"513992094b5edd9ee0b8b717eb973f8858bf961f","tid":2134510,"uid":359022,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:38:44.000Z","msg":"日頭好藍 黃昏好夢幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靚到好假"},{"pid":"207b077348dfa772e82844d91b819129b61aae61","tid":2134510,"uid":181549,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界無共狗大家會好過好多"},{"pid":"dac27a0b9398f9fe0d19def88ff504e7cb9b9669","tid":2134510,"uid":256330,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:58:39.000Z","msg":"支那=地球癌症"},{"pid":"3523f15b1db6a356e0f6da519022b325ae46f15a","tid":2134510,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T19:50:37